<L>__{10. between two guns night}
<A>__{boys no more than eight or nine years old play a game of 'jacks' with some sheep bones. addison, rye and swift are the powder monkeys who ferry powder from the hold to the guns during action.}
<L>__{11. berth deck night}
<A>__{a hundred hammocks swing like strange pods, close packed under the immense beams. most of the occupants are already asleep: here an arm, there a lolling head}
<C>__{hollar}
<D>__{lights out!}
<A>__{on the bosun's command, the last of the off duty men climb into their hammocks. the last lights are extinguished. only pullings' lamp remains, moving up the ladder to...}
